    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Extract structured data from the following resume text:\n\n{{ $json.clean_text }}\nCRITICAL:\n- If data is not clearly present → return null\n- Do NOT infer from assumptions\n- Do NOT complete partial phone numbers\n- Do NOT guess experience duration\n- Do NOT generate fake skills\n- Do NOT assume education details if missing\n\nIMPORTANT:\nThe input text may be messy, noisy, or incorrectly spaced due to OCR.\nReconstruct the meaning carefully, but do NOT guess or invent any missing information.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON. Do NOT include any explanation or extra text.\n\nSTRICT JSON FORMAT:\n\n\n{\n  \"phone_number\": null,\n  \"date_of_birth\": null,\n  \"gender\": null,\n  \"experience_years\": 0,\n  \"experience_months\": 0,\n  \"skills\": [],\n  \"education\": [\n    {\n      \"degree\": null,\n      \"institution\": null,\n      \"field_of_study\": null,\n      \"grade\": null,\n      \"percentage\": null,\n      \"start_year\": null,\n      \"end_year\": null,\n      \"currently_studying\": false\n    }\n  ],\n  \"confidence\": {\n    \"phone_number\": 0,\n    \"date_of_birth\": 0,\n    \"gender\": 0,\n    \"experience\": 0,\n    \"skills\": 0,\n    \"education\": 0\n  },\n  \"flags\": []\n}\n\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n- Output MUST be valid JSON (no comments, no extra text)\n- If any field is missing → return null (do NOT guess)\n- If multiple phone numbers → choose the most likely primary\n- Normalize phone number to Indian format: +91XXXXXXXXXX\n- Convert experience into:\n  - experience_years (integer)\n  - experience_months (integer)\n- Extract skills as a clean array (no duplicates, normalized casing)\n- Education must support multiple entries\n- If currently studying → currently_studying = true\n- Take start and end year properly \n- If experience is mentioned as date range → calculate carefully\n- If unclear → return 0 instead of guessing\n\nOCR-SPECIFIC HANDLING:\n- Fix broken words and spacing logically (e.g., \"P y t h o n\" → \"Python\")\n- Merge split lines into meaningful sentences\n- Ignore random symbols or OCR noise\n- If text is unclear → reduce confidence instead of guessing\n- - Preserve numbers exactly as seen (phone, percentage, years)\n- Do NOT merge unrelated text blocks\n- If OCR text is broken → reconstruct only when clearly obvious\n\nEDGE CASE HANDLING:\n- If phone not found → add flag: \"Phone number not found\"\n- If multiple phone numbers → add flag: \"Multiple phone numbers detected\"\n- If education incomplete → add flag: \"Education details incomplete\"\n- If DOB missing → add flag: \"Date of Birth not found\"\n\nEDUCATION DETAILS:\n- If detected_education is provided → use it as base and refine it\n- Do NOT ignore detected education entries\n- Improve structure but do NOT remove valid entries\n\nCONFIDENCE SCORING:\n- 90+ → clearly present in text\n- 50–80 → partially clear / inferred from context\n- <50 → weak, unclear, or OCR distorted\n\nDO NOT:\n- Do NOT hallucinate data\n- Do NOT assume missing values\n- Do NOT return text outside JSON",
